  schema:name "Settlement" ;
  schema:description "The four-cornered joint structure of values in the voidmath bilattice — composed of two independent axes (truth and knowledge) whose extremal positions give the four corners a predication value can occupy. The mathematical articulation of the relationality framework's settlement concept." ;
